OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FChance of a shower across the
OL,6,Fsouth this morning. Otherwise it will
OL,7,Fbe a dry day with some bright or sunny
OL,8,Fspells. A very warm day.
OL,9,
OL,10,CTonight:FA few showers will break out
OL,11,Facross Argyll through the evening and
OL,12,Fnight, occasionally heavy and
OL,13,Fthundery. Mostly dry elsewhere with
OL,14,Fvariable amounts of cloud.
OL,15,
OL,16,CFriday:FA cloudy day with some showery
OL,17,Frain across Argyll, just the odd
OL,18,Fshower further south. Brightening up
OL,19,Fin the south later.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
